{
  "stem": "3277.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came to the railroad station, with all-- with that-- with the new name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even I-- I met that guy from the same city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mark, Mark, Mark!",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, listen, I have to go someplace, I cannot talk to you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I haven't got the time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have the-- But anyway, I make it-- make it a little bit short, because it's a long story, actually.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- the car, Warsaw-Stockholm, was the last car which used to go-- it was vacation time, and about 10 cars, or 12 cars that used to go to the-- to the Baltic Sea.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- and the people were rushing into the car, to get the-- because they used to give out more tickets than people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was waiting someplace, when everybody went into the-- I went first into the car, Warsaw-Stockholm.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The guy saluted to me, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And even-- I was afraid-- even going out to railroad, I bought a Polish ticket, because I was afraid, even somebody would see that I'm showing a foreign passport.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But anyway, I make it very short.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then I came-- I went into the-- this was a few-- about 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I covered the window-- because it was a sleeping car, I covered the windows with the curtain, not that anybody be able to-- and the Scandinavian people were talking, but they were the-- but they were not like me.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, took a long-- finally, the car moved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I told the guy that I'm a nervous guy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then he said to me-- all of a sudden, he had some Valium or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I didn't know, at that time, what Valium is or anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, take one pill before you go to sleep at night.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
